data.description: Welcome to your dream home in West Monroe! This fantastic property boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and an open concept floor plan, offering ample space for comfortable living and entertaining. With a generous backyard, the possibilities are endless. Located in the charming community of West Monroe, this home is conveniently situated near schools, parks, shopping, and dining options. Don't miss the opportunity to make this spacious property your own - schedule a viewing today and imagine the possibilities for your future in this wonderful home!
